data.description: Welcome to this stunning and expansive two-story home in the Siena Subdivision, artfully crafted with a spacious and inviting floor plan; Upon entering, you'll immediately be captivated by the open consent design, with a floor plan that seamlessly combines style and functionality. The heart of the home is the entertainer's kitchen, boasting granite countertops, elegant shaker cabinetry, and a walk-in pantry. The primary suite is generously sized and includes a bathroom with dual vanity sinks, a garden tub, and a walk-in shower, and office/guestroom offering the perfect setup for comfort and flexibility when having guests over! The inviting great room showcases soaring ceilings and a cozy fireplace, adorned with expansive windows that flood the space with natural light, creating the perfect ambiance for gatherings with family and friends. Glass door effortlessly connects the indoors to the outdoors, leading you to the backyard oasis, complete with a covered patio and a stunning outdoor fireplace where you can unwind and relish in the tranquility of your surroundings. The Siena community provides useful amenities for all to enjoy including two swimming pools, a community center, playgrounds, sports courts, walking trails and much more. The location is highly convenient, as it's near the Tesla plant, the Kalahari indoor water park, and the Old Settlers outdoor park. Schedule a showing today!
